1080.jpg?t=1734107551","path_thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344030/ss_a718eb2141457eb8ebc6380cc24794d8731cd87c.600x338.jpg?t=1734107551"}],"short_description":"You are in a room without windows or doors. The TV dimly illuminates the room. What is this, a box? How to open it? After solving the riddle, you find the TV remote control. Click... a door appeared. You step into the darkness and hear laughter... turn around and find out what's behind the screen.","steam_appid":3344030,"support_info":{"email":"beshbarmakgames@gmail.com","url":""},"supported_languages":"English<strong>*</strong>, French, German, Spanish - Spain, Portuguese - Brazil, Simplified Chinese, Korean, Polish, Russian<strong>*</strong>, Japanese<br><strong>*</strong>languages with full audio support","type":"game","website":null}